Great place for a casual dinner!
The decor is warm (Thai theme) with comfortable booths and the service is great.
There is no long wait to be served your delicious meal.
The menu has a good variety (beef, pork, chicken, fish, seafood) with 4 degrees of heat.
The heat is real so be conservative!
I asked for medium/hot and would have been better with just medium.
Iced tea helped calm my mouth so np.
You really can't go wrong with anything you order and certainly a go-to place for us.

